ntinued support of the World Science Fiction Convention and the Hugo Awards. When much of the feedback I tend to hear is, more or less, \"Unless there's 50K or 100K people there, it isn't a real convention,\" and \"It's not successful unless you have to spend eight hours waiting in line for a one panel,\" it's nice to hear people pointing out what the value is in what is nowadays a \"midsize\" convention of \"only\" 3000-6000 attendees.<br /><br />I've attended every Worldcon since 1989, and I wouldn't trade them for any number of Monster Huge Standing In Line Conventions.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"5 years ago","ctime":"August 10 2011, 20:42:30 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://kevin-standlee.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"kevin_standlee","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"kevin_standlee","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://kevin-standlee.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"kevin_standlee","ctime_ts":"1313008950","tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/49583412/10744999","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/233477.html?thread=14498565#t14498565","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/233477.html?thread=14498565#t14498565","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/233477.html?thread=14498565#t14498565","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"skwidly","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://skwidly.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":14498565,"talkid":56635,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/233477.html?thread=14498565#t14498565","upictitle":"Skwid: Blue Y","article":"BWB really does throw the most reliably awesome party! It's not necessarily always the awesomest, but it's reliably awesome, and that's just what you need after wandering for a bit.<br /><br />See you there!","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"5 years ago","ctime":"August 10 2011, 23:36:20 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://skwidly.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"skwidly","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"skwidly","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://skwidly.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"skwidly","ctime_ts":"1313019380","tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/233477.html?thread=14498821#t14498821","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/233477.html?thread=14498821#t14498821","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/233477.html?thread=14498821#t14498821","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"jpclemen","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://jpclemen.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":14498821,"talkid":56636,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/233477.html?thread=14498821#t14498821","upictitle":"jpclemen: pic#0","article":"So after this tWoW reading, will the Ice and Fire sample on your website be updated to include it?","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"5 years ago","ctime":"August 11 2011, 00:06:46 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://jpclemen.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146